The Stanley Parable is a first person exploration game. You will play

as Stanley, and you will not play as Stanley. You will follow a story

you will not follow a story. You will have a choice, you will have no

choice. The game will end, the game will never end. Contradiction

follows contradiction, the rules of how games should work are broken

then broken again. This world was not made for you to understand

But as you explore, slowly, meaning begins to arise, the paradoxes

might start to make sense, perhaps you are powerful after all. The

game is not here to fight you; it is inviting you to dance



1. Extract release

2. Mount ISO

3. Install the game

4. Copy crack from the folder /PLAZA

5. Play
